### Installing Nextflow

open your terminal and create 
`mkdir usrbin`
`cd usrbin`
then run: `wget -qO- https://get.nextflow.io | bash`
`sudo nano /etc/paths` then type `export PATH=$PATH:/my/custom/path`,
`echo "$PWD"`
`nextflow -version`

